summary: The code performs a Subversion update, copies several Python files and data files to a specific directory, adds newly created or modified files to the repository, and commits the changes with a message "update".

details.comment: The code performs a Subversion update, copies several Python files and data files to a specific directory, adds newly created or modified files to the repository, and commits the changes with a message "update".
details.content:
svn update D:\project\XiDianProject\YH\04-编码\NetworkVisualize 
cp connectivity_matrix.xlsx integratedEnergySystemPrototypes.py system_topology_utils.py mini_data_log_utils.py jinan_changqing-hour.dat mini_ies_test.py mini_heat_system.py mini_refrigeration_system.py result_processlib.py demo_utils.py data_visualize_utils.py config.py cpExample.py README.md requirements.txt -t D:\project\XiDianProject\YH\04-编码\NetworkVisualize\
svn add D:\project\XiDianProject\YH\04-编码\NetworkVisualize\*
svn commit D:\project\XiDianProject\YH\04-编码\NetworkVisualize -m "update"
